TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
What have you heard of the Waterdhavian creatures on the loose?
Text: 풀려난 워터딥의 생명체들에 대해 들은 게 있습니까?

TextEng: Any strange events lately that you can think of?
Anything interesting going on in Blacklake?
You hear 'bout Waterdhavian creatures, maybe?
Any strange stuff happen?
What going on here?
Any idea where they could be if they came here?
Text: 그 생명체들이 여기로 왔다면 어디에 있을지 짐작가는 곳이 있습니까?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Has there been anything odd since the creatures escaped, that you remember?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 그 생명체들이 탈출한 뒤로 기억나는 이상한 일이 있습니까?

TextEng: You think where they go if they came, maybe?
Anything you consider odd?
Anyone in need of assistance that you know of?
Places of interest, perhaps?
Odd stuff?
Someone need help, maybe?
Neat places to go?
There's been no cases of the plague here at all?
Text: 여긴 울부짖는 죽음 역병 환자가 전혀 없다는 겁니까?

TextEng: No plague here at all?
Text: 여긴 울부짖는 죽음 역병 하나도 없어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now, telling me won't do any harm.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 자, 내게 말해도 해가 될 건 없어요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Tell me. Will hurt nobody.
What do you know about the plague?
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병에 대해 무엇을 아십니까?

TextEng: What you know 'bout plague?
Text: 울부짖는 죽음 역병에 대해 뭐 알아?

TextEng: I want to ask you something else.
Me have other question.
I need directions.
Me need directions.
Where is the nearest temple?
Is there a place to buy equipment nearby?
Text: 근처에 장비를 살 만한 곳이 있습니까?

TextEng: I'm looking for a good tavern.
Me look for temple.
Me need place to buy stuff.
Good place to drink?
Actually, I'd rather ask you about something else.
No, me have other question.
I made it past the gate, didn't I?
Watch your tone. I've had enough of being challenged.
Text: 말투 좀 조심하죠. 시비는 이제 지겨우니까.

TextEng: I am a member of the guard, working for Aribeth.
Me get past gate, no?
Watch tone! Me no like always being yelled at!
Text: 말투 조심! 나 맨날 소리치는 거 싫어!

TextEng: Me is a guard, work for Aribeth.
Yes, and to the Abyss with your orders, I'll go where I like.
Text: 그래, 그런 명령 따위는 지옥에 던져버려. 난 내 맘대로 갈 거니까.

TextEng: Yeah, and me no care about orders. Me go where me wants.
Text: 그래, 명령 따위 신경 안 써. 난 내가 가고 싶은 데로 가.

TextEng: Anything else?
Any more?
Yous can tell me, okay? We <race> kin.
Text: 너 말해줄 수 있어, 그렇지? 우리 <race> 동족이잖아.

TextEng: You can tell me. We're <race> kin.
